    "But children playing in the house, especially our young relatives when visiting, sometimes knocked off a boiling pot of food.",
    "My right leg has a scar from a burn from that baboor.",
    "Balcony For the first time, we have hot and cold running water.",
    "Balcony This makes Mother dance as she turns the faucet on and off.",
    "Balcony Dancing is the way she celebrates."
